UNGQONGQOSHE wezempilo kuleli uDkt Zweli Mkhize uthi amabandla ezenkolo azolekelela empini neCovid-19 kuleli kulandela isinqumo sikamengameli Cyril Ramaphosa sokuvulwa kwamasonto esigabeni sesithathu sokathaqa. Sishiye abaningi behlukene phakathi isinqumo sikaRamaphosa sokuvumela ukuthi ziqhubeke izinkonzo emabandleni kusukela ngenyanga ezayo inqobo nje uma kuzobakhona abantu abawu-50 kuphela enkonzweni. Nokho nasezinkundleni zokuxhumana akhona namakholwa azwakalise ukungagciliseki ngokuvulwa kwezikole ngokunjalo nokuvunyelwa kwabasebenzi ukuthi babuyele emsebenzini kodwa indlu yeNkosi inqatshelwa ukuba iqhubeke nomsebenzi wayo. Ephendulula imibuzo ngoLwesithathu ngemuva kwesimemezelo sikaRamaphosa sokuvulwa kwamasonto ngaphansi kwemithetho eqinile, uMkhize uthe zizobaluleka ezenkolo empini neCovid-19. "Sibathatha njengophathina bethu empini neCovid-19 abantu bezenkolo, ikakhulukazi ekuqinisekiseni ukuthi abantu bayayiguqula indlela abaziphatha ngayo," kusho uMkhize obonge abaholi bezenkolo abawuthobelile umthetho kathaqa.  We take the church and the faith based community as partners in the fight against covid19, particularly to ensure social behavioural change. #NationalAssemblyQuestions projections which estimate new infections and deaths as well as the resources needed for the response; the interventions if fully implemented that can flatten the curve; and the spatial models which can be used to identify hotspots. #NationalAssemblyQuestions It is estimated that the number of deaths could range between 34,000 to 50,000. All of these figures have also been challenged by other academics.they are open for debate by those who are specialists in this area.#NationalAssemblyQuestions